Author: sukadeltoro
Content:
Intelligence iNtegrated Analytical-Sensemaking-Anticipatory Framework:

1. Factual/Event Reporting: Facts, Events, Real Time
2. Evaluative-Analytical Production: Contexts, Insights, Factors, Drivers
3. Sensemaking-Assessment Estimates: Morphological Analysis-Aware (ALL DOMAINS contexts, Insights, Factors, Drivers), Assess (Size, Intent, Capabilities), Anticipate (General Implications in short, medium, long term; Actor-specific implications; Conclusion; Judgement; Recommendations)
4. Scenario-Anticipation: (All Implications, Situations, Trends, Threats, Behaviours; Measures/Countermeasures to prevent, mitigate, stabilise, and rehablitate from the events-of-scenario)
